Message.En: Abandoned House on the Outskirts and Good Intentions
Message.Jp: 外れの空き家と小さな善意

Message.En:
There's a vacant house that seems usable
with a bit of repair, but I haven't had time
to get the materials. If I had <LQVA>
<LQIM>, I could manage the rest.
Message.Jp:
少し手入れをすれば使えそうな空き家があるのに
修理のための材料を手に入れる暇が無いんだ
<LQIM>が<LQVA>個あれば
後は俺が何とかするんだがな
